column4:
Dear Sir/Ma,


My name is Chloe from MEIHUA GROUP INTERNATIONAL TRADING COMPANY, based in Hong Kong. We are an international procurement agency for companies in Asia and Europe.

We are currently looking for a large quantity of the products I have attached according to the order inquiry of our new customer that is of high urgency.

Please check the attachment and advise your best prices and earliest delivery schedule.

Also, please check our questions in the following:

         1) All products must not be compressed, in clean condition, no contaminants such as mud, no rubber,

             no tire residues.

         2) Please provide the FOB

         3) Please provide the CIF to Port Yantian

         4) Please provide the transaction procedure

         5) What is your in-stock quantity?

         6) What is the maximum quantity that can be provided each month?

 

I look forward to hearing from you soon.


Thank you

Chloe Kim

MEIHUA GROUP INTERNATIONAL TRADING (HONG KONG) CO., LTD.  

Registered address: Room D 10/F Tower A Billion Centre,

1 Wang Kwong Road, Kowloon Bay, Kowloon, Hong Kong

Email [REDACTED][REDACTED]  URL: www.meihuagrp.com <http://www.meihuagrp.com/> 

Tel: + 86 316-2359999 Fax: +86 316-2359679
